- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a model to address the problem and evaluates its performance. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with natural language annotations of visual relationships. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a less likely category, but possible as the paper deals with visual relationships in images.
